h3cUps.name: h3cUps
h3cUps.contactinfo: Platform Team H3C Technologies Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China Http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
h3cUps.description: This MIB describes the general information of UPS(Uninterrupted Power Supply) device.

H3cActionType.name: H3cActionType
H3cActionType.description: A control variable used to trigger an operator events, when read, always returns a value of invalid.

h3cUpsConfigEnable.name: h3cUpsConfigEnable
h3cUpsConfigEnable.description: This object identifies the operation which will make the UPS(Uninterrupted Power Supply)'s new configure become effective.

h3cUpsConfigTable.name: h3cUpsConfigTable
h3cUpsConfigTable.description: This table contains an entry for user to get some information about the UPS device.

h3cUpsConfigEntry.name: h3cUpsConfigEntry
h3cUpsConfigEntry.description: An entry containing management information applicable to a particular UPS.

h3cUpsIndex.name: h3cUpsIndex
h3cUpsIndex.description: This object identifies the index of h3cUpsConfigTable. The object identified by this index is the same object as identified by the same value of entPhysicalIndex.

h3cUpsType.name: h3cUpsType
h3cUpsType.description: This object identifies the type of UPS. The value 'emersonUart' means an EMERSON UPS support UART interface. The value 'mge' means a MGE UPS support ethernet interface. The value 'common' means a common UPS support standard UPSMIB. The value 'emersonEth' means an EMERSON UPS support ethernet interface. The value 'liebert' means a Liebert UPS support ethernet interface.

h3cUpsIpAddress.name: h3cUpsIpAddress
h3cUpsIpAddress.description: This object describes the address of UPS. The value of this object is invalid if the UPS do not support ethernet interface.

h3cUpsIpAddressType.name: h3cUpsIpAddressType
h3cUpsIpAddressType.description: This object describes the address type of UPS. The value of this object is invalid if the UPS do not support ethernet interface.
